.name
SMaus
.author
Stefan Sticht 
.version
1.17
.distribution
Shareware
.description
A highly configurable "SUN-mouse" utility, implemented as a commodity with
a graphical user interface.  It activates the window under the mouse
pointer if you move or after you have moved the mouse or if you press a
key.  You can specify titles of windows which shall not be deactivated
using wildcards.  Requires at least AmigaOS 2.04, uses locale.library if
available.  Includes english and german docs, german catalog file.  
